      • MyArrayListOp

        public MyArrayListOp()
        Constructs an empty array-based list with capacity set to the INITIAL_CAPACITY.

      • MyArrayListOp

        public MyArrayListOp(E[] eArr)
        Constructs an array-based list containing the elements in the specified array. If the array argument is non-empty, the capacity of this list is set to the list's size. However, if the array argument is empty, the capacity of this list is set to the INITIAL_CAPACITY.
        Parameters:
        eArr - array containing initial list elements
